    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. It runs like a charm and has been well-loved, so it's definitely ready for its next big adventure with you! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to message me if you want to take it for a spin!",
