    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a linear power band and crisp throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is tight, with the rear subframe inspected and reinforced to manage the torque output of the M-Variable differential. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with spirited use, the suspension geometry remains true, and the braking system utilizes ventilated rotors with plenty of life. This is a driver-focused specimen optimized for tactile feedback and longitudinal performance.",
