    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained, reliable vehicle that perfectly balances performance and comfort. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Deep Charcoal Metallic; while the paint retains a high gloss, there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, dime-sized door ding on the rear passenger panel consistent with careful daily use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with premium black leather seating. The interior is in great shape, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and navigation system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is solid. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles, with a fresh oil change and brake inspection performed last month. The tires currently have approximately 70% tread remaining. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and has a clean title in hand. I have a folder of service records ready for the next owner to review. It is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
