    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s ready for a new home and someone who will appreciate how smoothly it still handles. If you're looking for a dependable car that looks great and drives even better, this is the one for you! Come swing by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
